 actors welcome the decision|publisher=}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | [[Sri Lanka]]\n| [[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n| ''\u0ba8\u0bc0\u0baf\u0bbe''\n| [[Shakthi TV]]\n| {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| [[Sinhalese language|Sinhalese]]\n| ''\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dda\u0db8 \u0daf\u0da9\u0dba\u0db8''\n| [[Sirasa TV]]\n| {{N/A|}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2 | [[Vietnam]]\n| rowspan=2 | [[Vietnamese language|Vietnamese]]\n| ''X\u00e0 N\u1eef B\u00e1o Th\u00f9''\n| [[:vi:T\u1ed5ng C\u00f4ng ty Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh C\u00e1p Vi\u1ec7t Nam|Echannel (VTVCab5)]]\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thanhnien.vn/van-hoa/bom-tan-xuat-sac-nhat-2016-cua-an-do-len-song-truyen-hinh-viet-723143.html|title=\u2018Bom t\u1ea5n\u2019 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t 2016 c\u1ee7a \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 l\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t|language=vi-VN|access-date=2016-07-14}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''T\u00ecnh Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ki\u1ebfp R\u1eafn''\n| [[:vi:\u0110\u00e0i Ph\u00e1t thanh - Truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh V\u0129nh Long|THVL1]]\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thvl.vn/gioi-thieu-phim/phim-da-chieu/tinh-ng%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Di-ki%E1%BA%BFp-r%E1%BA%AFn/|title=T\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfp r\u1eafn \u2013 .:: \u0110\u00e0i Ph\u00e1t Thanh v\u00e0 Truy\u1ec1n H\u00ecnh V\u0129nh Long ::.|language=vi-VN|access-date=2019-08-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thvl.vn/gioi-thieu-phim/phim-da-chieu/tinh-ng%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Di-ki%E1%BA%BFp-r%E1%BA%AFn-ph%E1%BA%A7n-2/|title=T\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfp r\u1eafn \u2013 Ph\u1ea7n 2 \u2013 .:: \u0110\u00e0i Ph\u00e1t Thanh v\u00e0 Truy\u1ec1n H\u00ecnh V\u0129nh Long ::.|language=vi-VN|access-date=2019-08-28}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Thailand]]\n| [[Thai language|Thai]]\n| ''\u0e19\u0e32\u0e04\u0e34\u0e19''\n| [[Channel 3 (Thailand)|Channel 3]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ch3thailand.com/%E0%B8%8B%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%AA%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%8A%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%873/series/312/%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%99-%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%A7-%E0%B9%86-%